Message

As prophesied in the scriptures, the phase of 'Last Judgement' has started. The testing ground is of great "illusion (Mahamaya) . Kundalini is the indicator of our balance and wisdom. She will evaluate, correct and evolve us. Sahaja Yoga gives you a chance to be fully your meaning. Take Full advantage of it. Establish your attention in the Absolute (Atman) and achieve the eternal life in the Kingdom of God. This lies more in the capacities and subtleties of subtler people. Later on the gross may follow.The early Sahaja Yogis are the foundation of this Empire of God.

May God bless you all.

London, June, 1980
